PRINTFORMDL An oomukade who serves as the foreman of the Youkai Mountain's Dragon Gem mining operations. %HE_SHE([[百々世]],1)% works alongside
PRINTFORMDL %HIS_HER([[パルスィ]])% best friend Megumu Iizunamaru, Chimata Tenkyuu, and %CALLNAME:139% Kudamaki to manufacture Ability Cards.
PRINTFORMDL
PRINTFORMDL Although %HE_SHE([[百々世]])% calls %HIMSELF_HERSELF([[百々世]])% "The %PRINT_MALE("Prince:Princess", [[百々世]])% Who Slays Dragon Kings", nobody knows for sure if
PRINTFORMDL that's actually true. And nobody's willing to risk offending %HIM_HER([[百々世]])% by asking %HIM_HER([[百々世]])%, either, as %HE_SHE([[百々世]])%
PRINTFORMDL takes %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% honor very seriously.
PRINTFORMDL
PRINTFORMDL Oomukade are known and feared for their immense magical power and formidable physical strength. However, %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% is
