;※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※
;Custom dialogue settings, custom code
;※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※
;made it as a way to speed up the update process and separate simple flag updates from various customization options
;note: options start from 1!
@KOJO_OPTION_K142
;CALL KOJO_OPTION_ITEM("Dialogue setting customization", 1)

;process the input portion
@KOJO_OPTION_K142_RESULT_1
CALL K142_CONFIGURE
;RESETCOLOR because the last line in K142_CONFIGURE sets color for the upcoming texts
RESETCOLOR

;※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※
;"ENCOUNTER" events (extra syntax)
;"ENCOUNTER"系イベント（エクストラ構文）
;First Meeting
;※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※
@M_KOJO_ENCOUNTER_K142
;初対面、挨拶のタイミング
;TALENTの変更はここでどうぞ。
;経験の変更は齟齬が出る場合がありますので、CSVを修正し同梱する事を推奨します
CFLAG:[[百々世]]:K142EN_STARTING_VIRGINITY = THINKS_IS_VIRGIN([[百々世]])
IF TALENT:MASTER:追加種族 == 4
	CFLAG:[[百々世]]:K142EN_PLAYER_STARTING_RACE = 4
ELSE
	CFLAG:[[百々世]]:K142EN_PLAYER_STARTING_RACE = IS_NONHUMAN(MASTER)
ENDIF

PRINTFORMW 「Yo! You the new %PRINT_MALE("guy", MASTER)% everyone's talkin' about?」
PRINTFORMDW A %PRINT_MALE("man", [[百々世]])% with greyish-blue hair is leaning on a shovel and grinning at you.
PRINTFORMDW You can't help but notice how sharp %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% teeth are.
PRINTFORMW 「The name's %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]%. %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% Himemushi. Nice to meetcha!」
PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% extends a hand. Her grin grows even wider.
PRINTFORMDL
PRINTFORMDW Shake it?
CALL ASK_YN()
IF !RESULT
	PRINTFORMDW You take %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]%'s hand.
	PRINTFORMDW The first thing you notice is how rough and callused her hands are.
	PRINTFORMDW The second thing you notice is how unbelievably strong %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% grip is.
	IF IS_NONHUMAN(MASTER) || ABL:MASTER:戦闘能力 >= ABL:[[百々世]]:戦闘能力
		PRINTFORMDW It's like a vise. An ordinary person would be in agony right now.
		PRINTFORMDW But you're not an ordinary person.
		PRINTFORMDW You tighten your grip to match hers and give her a firm handshake.
		PRINTFORMW 「Damn, you're strong!」
		PRINTFORMDW %HE_SHE([[百々世]],1)% stares at your intertwined hands, a glint of admiration in her eyes.
		PRINTFORMW 「Brave as hell, too. The tengu always try to talk their way outta shakin' my hand.」
		PRINTFORMW 「You and me should have a Danmaku match sometime.」
		PRINTFORMW 「There's nothin' more fun than a good scrap!」
		CALL CHANGE_CFLAG(GETNUM(CFLAG, "好感度"), [[百々世]], 200)
	ELSEIF TALENT:MASTER:痛覚 == -1 || PERCENT(10 * ABL:MASTER:戦闘能力)
		PRINTFORMDW And the third thing you notice is the white-hot agony as her hand clenches around yours like a vise.
		PRINTFORMDW Pain lances through your fingers. You bite your lip to stifle an agonized yell.
	 	PRINTFORMDW The bones in your hand grind together. You swear you feel something break.
		PRINTFORMDW And you swear you saw a disappointed look on her face, just for a second.
		PRINTFORMDW Momoyo tries to let go of your hand, but you force yourself to hold on.
		PRINTFORMDW You don't want to look weak in front of %HIM_HER([[百々世]])%.
		PRINTFORMDW Gritting your teeth, you ignore the pain and force yourself to give %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% a firm handshake.
		PRINTFORMDW Momoyo lets out a low whistle.
		PRINTFORMW 「Damn, you're strong!」
		PRINTFORMW 「The tengu always try to talk their way outta shakin' my hand, but you went right for it!」
		PRINTFORMW 「And even when I realized I was squeezin' too hard and tried to let go, you held on like it was nothin'!」
		PRINTFORMW 「You may not have the strength of an oomukade... but you've definitely got the soul of one.」
		PRINTFORMW 「...Uh, your hand's gonna be okay, right?」
		PRINTFORMDW You gingerly flex your hand and decide that it probably will.
		PRINTFORMW 「Good. That'd be one hell of an awkward first impression.」
		CALL CHANGE_CFLAG(GETNUM(CFLAG, "好感度"), [[百々世]], 300)
	ELSEIF TALENT:MASTER:痛覚 == 1
		GOTO EPIC_HANDSHAKE_FAIL
	ELSE
		$EPIC_HANDSHAKE_FAIL
		PRINTFORMDW And the third thing you notice is the white-hot agony as her hand clenches around yours like a vise.
		PRINTFORMDW You let out an agonized yell as pain lances through your fingers.
		PRINTFORMDW The bones in your hand grind together. You swear you feel something break.
		PRINTFORMDW And you swear you saw a disappointed look on her face, just for a second.
		PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% lets go of your hand and examines it.
		PRINTFORMW 「I \@ IS_NONHUMAN(MASTER) ? didn't realize I was crushin' your hand. # forgot how fragile you humans are.\@ 」
		PRINTFORMW （And I was goin' easy on %HIM_HER(MASTER)%, too...）
		PRINTFORMW 「I didn't break anything, did I?」
		PRINTFORMDW You gingerly flex your hand and decide that no, she didn't.
		PRINTFORMW 「Good. That'd be one hell of an awkward first impression.」
		PRINTFORMW 「But I gotta say, there ain't many people out there who'd shake an oomukade's hand.」
		PRINTFORMW 「Except oni, and they're almost as strong as we are.」
		PRINTFORMDW She gives you an approving nod, and a small smile tugs at the corner of her lips.
		CALL CHANGE_CFLAG(GETNUM(CFLAG, "好感度"), [[百々世]], 100)
		LOCAL = 1
	ENDIF
	PRINTFORMW 「Anyway...」
ELSE
	PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% frowns at you and awkwardly lowers %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% hand.
	PRINTFORMW (Brave enough to talk to an oomukade, but not brave enough to shake her hand...)
	PRINTFORMDW %HE_SHE([[百々世]],1)% narrows %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% eyes, leans forward, and stares at you.
	PRINTFORMDW There's a mix of emotions in her dark gray eyes. Curiosity, amusement, a little disdain...
	PRINTFORMDW The two of you stare at each other for a few tense seconds.
	PRINTFORMDW You open your mouth to say something and break the tension, but she cuts you off.
ENDIF
PRINTFORMW 「I'm the Rainbow Dragon Cave's foreman. I work in the mines, diggin' up Dragon Gems.」
IF TIME >= 930 && TIME < 960
	PRINTFORMW 「And now that I mention it, I gotta get back to work soon.」
	PRINTFORMW 「Don't want Iizunamaru chewin' me out for slackin' off.」
ENDIF
IF LOCAL
	PRINTFORMW 「Although you ain't that strong, so I'd recommend you stay away.」
	SIF !IS_NONHUMAN(MASTER)
		PRINTFORMW 「It's hard work and there's no air down there. And you humans gotta breathe, right?」
	PRINTFORMW 「But if you really wanna get stronger, I'd be glad to work out with ya.」
ELSE
	PRINTFORMW 「If you wanna give me a hand, I'd appreciate it. I'll even let you keep a few as payment, if Iizunamaru's cool with it.」
	PRINTFORMW 「And you can keep anything else you find. All we care about is Dragon Gems.」
ENDIF
PRINTFORMW 「OK, that's enough about me. What about you, uh... crap, I never got your name.」
PRINTFORMW 「%CALLNAME:MASTER%, huh? Got it.」
PRINTFORMW 「What about you, %CALLNAME:MASTER%?」
PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% leans on %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% shovel again and grins another toothy grin.
PRINTFORMDL 
PRINTFORMDL Some of %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]%'s traits can be changed. Would you like to configure %HIM_HER([[百々世]])%?
CALL ASK_YN()
SIF !RESULT
	CALL K142_CONFIGURE
RETURN 1

