		PRINTFORMW 「Oh man, I must be the happiest oomukade in Gensokyo...」
		PRINTFORMDW %HE_SHE([[百々世]],1)% takes your hand and gives it a tight squeeze.
		PRINTFORMW 「So... you wanna come back to my place?」
		PRINTFORMW 「I got some top-shelf sake I've been savin' for a special occasion, and I can't think of anything more special than this!」
		RETURN 1
	ENDIF
	;-------------------------------------------------
	;Confession rejected
	;告白失敗
	;記入チェック（=0, 非表示、1, 表示）
	LOCAL:1 = 1
	;-------------------------------------------------
	IF LOCAL:1 && ARG == 2
		PRINTFORMW 「...Oh.」
